Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Typhoon 13 is continuing to the north with extraordinary force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami Daitou entered the storm's area of effect at around 11PM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Its effect on transport systems in various areas is currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.04,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: "Unko" in Japanese is "poo". "Unkou" means "running".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV says the bullet trains are doing a poo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "doing a poo"! "Running"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Running!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they said that normal bullet train service is "running", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means they're working like they normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo, woo! The trains are doing a poo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go and do a poo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is predicted that Typhoon 13 will\Ngradually shift its course towards the east...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and land in the Tokai area as evening turns into night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They said a typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. They come around every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.34,Alt,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No toilet paper left?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a really amazing one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring a ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They do say boys don't mature as fast as girls, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She must really have it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up early today, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kouki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave just the right amount of space where I drew the circles, it'll look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, how much is "just the right amount"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How many centimetres? How many millimetres?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to draw these circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave the rest for homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For your next class, everyone in the first year will be drawing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather outside beside your own morning glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are sandbags really that heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even the afternoon, and I'm already burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just our luck that we have a bunch of\Nsamples to ship out on top of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My kids' educational insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But they're still babies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be worth it to get insurance if I waited until they were older.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid for mine, too, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I doubt my kid will make it to university.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got two kids, so it's tough going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is still so young that we've\Ngot to worry about daycare fees, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Outgrows his clothes right away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, we're lucky enough to get pensions and health insurance, even though we're not with a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about life insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife took care of that before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine pays a lump sum if I die, and hers is tied to her savings account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty basic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys really are dads, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much insurance costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid next door is so loud that we want to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kind of makes you wonder what you're working for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take a good look at us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when you get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a girlfriend, anyway, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that, but no matter how much they complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can tell they're perfectly content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine any of them ever becoming like Rin's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down and draw like you're supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your drawing board?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ground is flat, so I don't really need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not acceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're told to bring something, you bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, your picture's really good, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, it's amazing! So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The colours of these two flowers are slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's reflected in Rin-san's drawing, with a purple flower and a blue one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was observant of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun and the others are messing around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's drawing time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your morning glories are amazing, Kouki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste not to sketch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi-sensei, {\i1}I'm{\i0} his teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-san, why do you always do your best to disturb everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down and start drawing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And no funny faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have Kouki's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kouki-san! You boys! Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down and draw properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them distract you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun's always acting up, and he's scary when he gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll bully you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We were at nursery together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have to meet your kids at six, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're cutting it close today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's get this done and dusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, looks like you got soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Your father's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and get Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's gotten stronger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wanted to get here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I the last to pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you and Kouki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a storm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's pretty wild outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!{Aww, Kouki is sometimes cute... <3}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but there's really no way that we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But the wind's only going to get more and more fierce, so can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Nitani-san and see if it's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and then pass her over to you for confirmation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you put it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll be going home early, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous. Get behind me and follow closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and get you towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the storm shutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! Let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Don't get your fingers caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like a secret base, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rinse it out. Keep your eyes shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Dry the rest yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, your back is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening! It's Nitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So they let you out of work early?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was sticking my nose in where I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! You've been such a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kouki got soaked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know how to begin to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me yours, Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you to call him "Daikichi-san"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Daikichi" is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more comfortable with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best for Daikichi to just be Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at that, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use a knife, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already a big girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi works with the flame, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never help out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lend you my knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Onions are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch! Go and rinse your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These are supposed to be... hamburgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll taste fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! The eggs are hard boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you peel them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That Rin... She's getting so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, do you love your mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... She's kind of an old nag, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a definite feeling of content here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even say "let's eat".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, use your chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm just gathering it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Food always tastes better when everyone eats together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat here again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave the dishes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, it hit him on the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to give Kouki many opportunities like this until now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad we had this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! We should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei said we didn't need those circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to seem him smile like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got off work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's raising a child on her own, just like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Come here a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better be off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I call a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But Reina-chan and her mum stayed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We had fun, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The typhoon's gone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:13.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun's here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's early again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:24.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to open the storm shutters...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky's as clear as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun, we're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, cooking in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki's mom made me a perfect gruel for a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You start with konbu soup, than you put in carrots, mushrooms, pumpkin, and onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you cut in small pieces of potato and boil it gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you take it from the fire and season it with salt and soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Last you put in the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "Stomach Flu."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eat.
